{"tid":569924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（Hehe)許廷鏗胡鴻鈞疑結伴遊冰島","createTime":"2018-02-23T07:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T09:32:27.000Z","uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aed5c6e78988310f6fe3b503ccd3e457f909fea1","tid":569924,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"歌手許廷鏗(Alfred)與<span style=\"color: red;\">同性密友</span>胡鴻鈞(Hubert)感情要好，更多次傳出緋聞。最近二人都「巧合」地在Instagram上載了在冰島拍攝的照片，雖然照片都是他們的單人照，但兩人的照片背景非常相似，二人疑似結伴到冰島旅行。<br />\n<br />\n其實Alfred早前出席活動時，已表示農曆新年會去旅行，並指若在外地碰見Hubert，會自拍甫上網及一齊食飯，未知是否暗示會遇見對方呢？去旅行期間，Alfred就真的遇見兩位朋友，還上載了合照。有大批網民留言話：「快點影下你同Hubert啦」、「既然咁有緣，撞埋Hubert了」、「全人類等緊你'撞'hubert」，非常搞笑！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1146881/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F1146881%2F&d=nGmPlKXyr6%2Bq9HMFUFVD5ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=fd394dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F1146881%2F&h=c7c96006\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1146881/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c2a9e45d91558233fac2f71688e76d2f66d4e3","tid":569924,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"撞撞撞咁好撞 屎忽撞棍呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605f961788096bbfebeb03dbc9be3166c60805a2","tid":569924,"uid":77134,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"去旅行一定要同異性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"f4061dcec74d4f1cb7a0494b30220beb06f2b3c5","tid":569924,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo